tabule
======
Alexandre Isoard <alexandre.isoard@gmail.com>
v1.1.0, May 2012

Transform tabulations into spaces ensuring both alignment and indentation

INSTALL
-------
To compile:

 $ make

To install:

 # make install

or to install to a custom path

 $ make PREFIX=<custom path> install

